.chronicle.com/article/LivingLearning-the/35803|journal=The Chronicle of Higher Education|volume=|pages=|via=The Chronicle of Higher Education}}</ref>\n* \u201cCharles Klauder\u2019s Brilliant Invisible Hand.\u201d [[The Chronicle of Higher Education]], March 25, 2005<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Halsband|first=Frances|date=25 March 2005|title=Charles Klauder's Brilliant Invisible Hand|url=https://www.chronicle.com/article/Charles-Klauders-Brilliant/2122|journal=The Chronicle of Higher Education|volume=|pages=|via=The Chronicle of Higher Education}}</ref>\n* \u201cCampuses in Place\u201d In Places Journal: Considering the Place of Campus'','' Vol. 17, Issue 1, Winter 2005<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Halsband|first=Frances|date=Winter 2005|title=Campuses in Place|url=https://placesjournal.org/print-archive/considering-the-place-of-campus/?cn-reloaded=1|journal=Places Journal|volume=17|pages=|via=Places Journal}}</ref>\n* \"Introduction to The Inhabited Landscape: An Exhibition,\u201d Places Journal, Volume 4/4, 1988<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Halsband|first=Frances|date=1988|title=Introduction to The Inhabited Landscape: An Exhibition|url=https://placesjournal.org/assets/legacy/pdfs/the-inhabited-landscape-introduction.pdf|journal=Places Journal|volume=4|pages=|via=Places Journal}}</ref>\n\n=== Illustrations ===\n\n* Halsband, Frances (Illustrator), ''Publishing: a writer's memoir,'' by Gail Godwin, Bloomsbury, 2015<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.worldcat.org/title/publishing-a-writers-memoir/oclc/907965981&referer=brief_results|title=Publishing: a writer's memoir|last=Godwin|first=Gail|date=2016|website=WorldCat|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=6 April 2020}}</ref>\n* Halsband, Frances (Illustrator), \u201cUlster County Ghosts,\u201d by Gail Godwin, ''Kingston: The IBM Years,'' The Friends of Historic Kingston/Black Dome Press, Delmar NY, 2014<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.worldcat.org/title/kingston-the-ibm-years/oclc/878837609&referer=brief_results|titl