ate\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n! scope=\"col\"| Label\n! scope=\"col\"| {{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Various\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 19 January 2018\n| {{hlist|[[Music download|Digital download]]|[[Streaming media|streaming]]}}\n| Darenote\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/hear-kylie-minogues-euphoric-new-song-dancing-w515625|title=Hear Kylie Minogue's Euphoric New Song 'Dancing' Off New LP 'Golden'|publisher=[[Rolling Stone]]|date=19 January 2018|accessdate=19 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australia\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Contemporary hit radio]]\n| {{hlist|Liberator|[[BMG Rights Management|BMG]]}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://themusicnetwork.com/news/most-added-kylie-was-and-always-will-be-radios-treasure|title=Most Added: Kylie was, and always will, be radio's treasure|publisher=The Music Network|date=25 January 2018|accessdate=25 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Italy\n| rowspan=\"2\"| BMG\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://radiodate.it/radio-date/kylie-minogue-dancing-177299-19-01-2018-radiodate/|title=Kylie Minogue - Dancing RadioDate|publisher=Radio Airplay FM|date=19 January 2018|accessdate=19 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| United Kingdom\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b09lt16j|title=Kylie Minogue World Exclusive and Winnie the Pooh|publisher=[[BBC Radio 2]]|date=19 January 2018|accessdate=25 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\"| Various\n| 23 February 2018\n| {{hlist|Digital download|streaming}} (Initial Talk remix)\n| rowspan=\"3\"| Darenote\n| <ref name=\"initial\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/50eFKER8Q5s0q3LP7oeklx|title=Dancing (Initial Talk Remix)|publisher=[[Spotify]]|accessdate=9 March 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2 March 2018\n| {{hlist|Digital download|streaming}} ([[Illyus & Barrientos]] remix)\n| <ref name=\"illyus\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/1tdVedvLnQ7GCAIECfqSEF\n|title=Dancing (Illyus & Barrie